&lt;h2 id="just-enough-microservices">Just Enough Microservices&lt;/h2>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>Microservices are independently deployable services modelled around a business domain.&lt;/p>&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;h3 id="independent-deployability">Independent deployability&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>This allows us to change a microservice and deploy it into production without having to utilise or change any other services.
This property requires loose coupling (&amp;lsquo;change one service without having to change anything else&amp;rsquo;).
We use stable contracts to help guide how we find the service boundaries.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>